Description: LexOPS is a package for generating controlled matched items for factorial designs. It has an inbuilt dataset of word features for word stimuli in Psychology experiments. Full documentation is available at <https://jackedtaylor.github.io/LexOPSdocs/>. There is a shiny app built with GUIs for most package functionality.
